loRace-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/26105155/Rouvy-Skoda-Dresden-VeloRace-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/26105155/Rouvy-Skoda-Dresden-VeloRace-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/26105155/Rouvy-Skoda-Dresden-VeloRace-696x464.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/26105155/Rouvy-Skoda-Dresden-VeloRace-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/26105155/Rouvy-Skoda-Dresden-VeloRace-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><ul><li><b>Ride historic Dresden Velorace tomorrow from home, on Rouvy</b> – The ŠKODA Velorace in Dresden (SVRD) is the most beautiful city cycling tour in Germany. The open virtual race on ROUVY invites everyone to discover the city from home and challenge former UCI World Champion Bert Grabsch this weekend, June 27. Register now for Sunday morning’s (09:30 CEST) open race. <a href=\"https://rouvy.com/events/race/53836\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rouvy.com</a></li></ul></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"fcc8e66579790f45ce079673865f234e1d461aa196b390f4c03fd49b7eebae15","category":"Cycling"}